    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/f6eb1434ae4becb8af1b276f9b9177c5.avif?t=1758113613\" width=800 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《CatCat》是一款休闲、治愈的养猫模拟游戏。你可以饲养不同品种的猫咪，给它们喂食，抚摸它们。当然你还可以自由的更改空间布局，摆放家具和更换墙壁颜色，打造属于自己和猫咪的小天地。没有目标，没有压力，轻松惬意地和猫咪们窝在一起。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >蠢萌的电子小猫</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中你可以通过清理便便和毛团，或者销毁家具来获得猫蛋，并孵化出不同品种的猫咪。给他们喂食，等待它们成长，它们也会给你带来小惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/7be3c75495dce6f8191e7ff6d95b8b6a.poster.avif?t=1758113613\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/7be3c75495dce6f8191e7ff6d95b8b6a.webm?t=1758113613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/7be3c75495dce6f8191e7ff6d95b8b6a.mp4?t=1758113613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义房间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在空间中自由摆放地板，并用家具填充每一个角落。搭配不同地板、墙壁纹理，打造独特空间氛围。为猫咪打造独一无二的舒适生活环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/a1308da4a5ac083f8348ece238b2ea82.poster.avif?t=1758113613\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/a1308da4a5ac083f8348ece238b2ea82.webm?t=1758113613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/a1308da4a5ac083f8348ece238b2ea82.mp4?t=1758113613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各种各样的道具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕获扭蛋精灵发现种类繁多的家具和道具，收集它们填充你的图鉴。或与它们互动看看能产生什么化学反应？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/94655f1537a7a813a3cd93d18a78409a.poster.avif?t=1758113613\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/94655f1537a7a813a3cd93d18a78409a.webm?t=1758113613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120890/extras/94655f1537a7a813a3cd93d18a78409a.mp4?t=1758113613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
